snippet: Confusion surrounded the election of Ahmed Maitiq as prime minister, dealing another blow to a transitional government that has struggled to find coherence.
abstract: Confusion surrounds election of Ahmed Maitiq as prime minister of Libya, dealing another blow to a transitional government that has struggled to find coherence.
